		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Saint James Harris Wood</span></strong> grew up in Hawaii and California, playing blues and punk rock and writing stories. While touring with his band, he fell in with a group of heroin smokers, which led to his incarceration for robbing banks with a toy gun. Correspondence can be sent to Saint James Harris Wood T30027, P.O. Box 8101, CMC East-6240, San Luis Obispo, California, 93409. His music can be found at <a href="http://www.darklyabsurd.com">www.darklyabsurd.com</a>.</p><a href="/contributors/saint-james-harris-wood" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
